00:35:01,020 --> 00:35:03,560
 A živim u stvarnosti

901
00:35:03,560 --> 00:35:05,180
 i svjesna sam da šta god rekla,

902
00:35:05,180 --> 00:35:06,220
 ljudi opet ljude dijele

903
00:35:06,220 --> 00:35:07,500
 na ljevo i na desno.

904
00:35:07,500 --> 00:35:09,820
 I sad mogla reći

905
00:35:09,820 --> 00:35:10,720
 ljevo ne znači ljevo,

906
00:35:10,720 --> 00:35:11,300
 nego to i to,

907
00:35:11,300 --> 00:35:12,300
 desno ne znači desno,

908
00:35:12,300 --> 00:35:12,680
 nego to i to.

909
00:35:12,680 --> 00:35:13,560
 Ali to je orijentacija.

910
00:35:13,560 --> 00:35:15,020
 Da, ljudima to je orijentacija.

911
00:35:15,020 --> 00:35:17,620
 Ja nemam nikav problem

912
00:35:17,620 --> 00:35:18,700
 s time da budem

913
00:35:18,700 --> 00:35:19,920
 ili ljevo ili desno.

914
00:35:19,920 --> 00:35:21,720
 Da pa će,

915
00:35:21,720 --> 00:35:23,620
 što smatram da ispremo,

916
00:35:23,620 --> 00:35:24,280
 to zagovaram.

917
00:35:24,280 --> 00:35:25,500
 Ja sam negdje centar

918
00:35:25,500 --> 00:35:26,960
 i sad ne mislim da to je

919
00:35:26,960 --> 00:35:28,240
 ispražnjena funkcija

920
00:35:28,240 --> 00:35:29,360
 i ono ljudi isto,

921
00:35:29,360 --> 00:35:30,880
 mislim ja isto da to nisam,

922
00:35:30,880 --> 00:35:31,860
 ja sad kad bi neko rekao

923
00:35:31,860 --> 00:35:32,280
 da je centar,

924
00:35:32,280 --> 00:35:34,080
 ja bih da reći šta si.

925
00:35:34,500 --> 00:35:35,580
 Nemo, svi su centar,

926
00:35:35,580 --> 00:35:36,460
 desni centar,

927
00:35:36,460 --> 00:35:37,560
 ono, svi su centar,

928
00:35:37,560 --> 00:35:38,420
 ljevi centar,

929
00:35:38,420 --> 00:35:39,200
 desni centar,

930
00:35:39,200 --> 00:35:40,440
 svi love u mutnom

931
00:35:40,440 --> 00:35:41,360
 jer misle da se tamo

932
00:35:41,360 --> 00:35:41,780
 svi negdje nalaze.

933
00:35:41,780 --> 00:35:42,240
 A Andrej Plenković je

934
00:35:42,240 --> 00:35:42,720
 desni centar.

935
00:35:42,720 --> 00:35:44,500
 Da, on je i desni

936
00:35:44,500 --> 00:35:45,340
 i ljevi centar.

937
00:35:45,340 --> 00:35:45,860
 I ljevi centar, da.

938
00:35:45,860 --> 00:35:46,940
 I centar desnog

939
00:35:46,940 --> 00:35:47,780
 i ljevog centara.

940
00:35:47,780 --> 00:35:49,160
 I centar svega.

941
00:35:49,160 --> 00:35:50,380
 Sigurno središte toga,

942
00:35:50,380 --> 00:35:51,200
 da, točno tako.

943
00:35:51,200 --> 00:35:51,820
 Sigurno središte toga svega.

944
00:35:51,820 --> 00:35:53,020
 Pomisle smo na isto, da.

945
00:35:53,020 --> 00:35:54,340
 Da, da, slažim se.

946
00:35:54,340 --> 00:35:58,780
 Da, sad, kako ja to vidim,

947
00:36:00,100 --> 00:36:01,480
 uz tu dozu samokritike

948
00:36:01,480 --> 00:36:02,440
 koja je stvarno nužna.

949
00:36:02,440 --> 00:36:06,000
 Ja imam dosta umjerene stavove

950
00:36:06,000 --> 00:36:08,080
 i pokušavam pronaći

951
00:36:08,080 --> 00:36:09,500
 neku sredinu

952
00:36:09,500 --> 00:36:11,320
 između tih krajnosti.

953
00:36:11,320 --> 00:36:13,680
 Možda sam po nekim stvarima

954
00:36:13,680 --> 00:36:14,680
 čak i liberalna

955
00:36:14,680 --> 00:36:19,400
 u odnosu na većinu

956
00:36:19,400 --> 00:36:20,400
 s kojom sam okružena.

957
00:36:20,400 --> 00:36:22,320
 S druge strane...

958
00:36:22,320 --> 00:36:23,060
 Kako ćemo, na primjer?

959
00:36:23,060 --> 00:36:24,060
 Pa, ne znam.

960
00:36:24,060 --> 00:36:26,560
 Sad bi trebalo ići

961
00:36:26,560 --> 00:36:28,800
 od pitanja do pitanja, ali...

962
00:36:28,800 --> 00:36:29,620
 Ne, dobro, misle sam...

963
00:36:29,620 --> 00:36:32,060
 Da, morali bi postaviti

964
00:36:32,060 --> 00:36:32,840
 pojedinačno pitanje,

965
00:36:32,840 --> 00:36:34,600
 ali imam uopćeniti takav dojam

966
00:36:34,600 --> 00:36:36,840
 da se...

967
00:36:36,840 --> 00:36:39,200
 Ne doživljavam se

968
00:36:39,200 --> 00:36:40,780
 ono klasično konzervativnom.

969
00:36:40,780 --> 00:36:42,560
 Ali postoji ta jedna razlika

970
00:36:42,560 --> 00:36:45,060
 što je meni konzervativizam jasan

971
00:36:45,060 --> 00:36:45,840
 i prihvatljiv

972
00:36:45,840 --> 00:36:47,780
 i smatram ga racionalnim.

973
00:36:47,780 --> 00:36:50,680
 A kod nas je uvriježeno

974
00:36:50,680 --> 00:36:53,340
 razmišljati o konzervativcima,

975
00:36:53,340 --> 00:36:55,080
 pogotovo iz intelektualne pozicije,

976
00:36:55,080 --> 00:36:56,300
 kao nazadnim budalama.

977
00:36:56,300 --> 00:36:57,740
 Mislim, to je i medijska slika

978
00:36:57,740 --> 00:36:58,360
 koja se stvara.

979
00:36:58,360 --> 00:36:59,180
 I sad...

980
00:36:59,180 --> 00:37:01,080
 S kojom se malo koji konzervativac

981
00:37:01,080 --> 00:37:02,540
 identificira to uopće može.

982
00:37:02,540 --> 00:37:04,980
 Da, i sad se onda

983
00:37:04,980 --> 00:37:06,180
 u takvoj situaciji

984
00:37:06,180 --> 00:37:08,480
 gdje meni taj dialog

985
00:37:08,480 --> 00:37:10,620
 normalan i razumljiv,

986
00:37:10,620 --> 00:37:13,500
 onda mene uvijek

987
00:37:13,500 --> 00:37:15,340
 svrstava na jednu stranu.

988
00:37:15,340 --> 00:37:18,260
 Dakle, što je kod nas

989
00:37:18,260 --> 00:37:19,580
 nekakva pozicija centra?

990
00:37:19,580 --> 00:37:21,600
 Dakle, kod nas se to

991
00:37:21,600 --> 00:37:23,160
 onda svrstava u desni centar

992
00:37:23,160 --> 00:37:24,480
 kad kažete da mi startamo

993
00:37:24,480 --> 00:37:25,820
 od domovinskog rata,

994
00:37:26,140 --> 00:37:27,860
 da smo antitotalitarno nastrojeni

995
00:37:27,860 --> 00:37:29,680
 i da smatramo domovinski rato

996
00:37:29,680 --> 00:37:32,140
 početkom Hrvatske.

997
00:37:32,820 --> 00:37:35,220
 Znači, bitno je tu

998
00:37:35,220 --> 00:37:37,300
 postaviti neke granice

999
00:37:37,300 --> 00:37:39,280
 i u politici kada ste vi,

1000
00:37:39,280 --> 00:37:41,140
 vi onda ne propitujete samo stvari,

1001
00:37:41,140 --> 00:37:42,940
 nego i zagovarate određene vrijednosti.

1002
00:37:42,940 --> 00:37:44,100
 Morate zauzimati

1003
00:37:44,100 --> 00:37:45,960
 stavove o tomo što smatrate

1004
00:37:45,960 --> 00:37:47,080
 važnijem u društvu.

1005
00:37:47,080 --> 00:37:48,960
 Dakle, mi smo tu

1006
00:37:48,960 --> 00:37:49,800
 nedvosmisleni

1007
00:37:49,800 --> 00:37:50,760
 i tu se slažem

1008
00:37:50,760 --> 00:37:52,000
 s ostatkom svoga kluba.

1009
00:37:52,000 --> 00:37:54,180
 Dakle, sve ostalo

1010
00:37:54,180 --> 00:37:54,760
 mogu odgovarati

1011
00:37:54,760 --> 00:37:55,700
 na pojedinačna pitanja.

1012
00:37:55,800 --> 00:37:57,240
 Zapravo, evo, sad ćemo opet morati

1013
00:37:57,240 --> 00:37:58,200
 vrati se na početak

1014
00:37:58,200 --> 00:37:59,620
 onoga o čemu sam govorila,

1015
00:37:59,620 --> 00:38:01,520
 da je pitanje što kod nas znači

1016
00:38:01,520 --> 00:38:02,820
 desno

1017
00:38:02,820 --> 00:38:05,160
 i što kod nas znači ljevo.

1018
00:38:05,160 --> 00:38:07,040
 Ali, recimo, dobro,

1019
00:38:07,040 --> 00:38:08,580
 razumijem i slažem se s tom

1020
00:38:08,580 --> 00:38:09,020
 oko ovoga,

1021
00:38:09,020 --> 00:38:10,060
 ali evo, da ti postavim sad

1022
00:38:10,060 --> 00:38:10,780
 konkretno pitanje

1023
00:38:10,780 --> 00:38:12,060
 o pobačaju.

1024
00:38:12,060 --> 00:38:13,760
 Dakle, ti si, dakle,

1025
00:38:13,760 --> 00:38:15,140
 zauzela poziciju,

1026
00:38:15,140 --> 00:38:15,680
 odnosno,

1027
00:38:15,680 --> 00:38:18,140
 prihvaćaš stav znanosti,

1028
00:38:18,140 --> 00:38:20,280
 da je život počinje za čećem,

1029
00:38:20,280 --> 00:38:20,920
 a isto vremeno,

1030
00:38:20,920 --> 00:38:21,680
 kad se razgovara

1031
00:38:21,680 --> 00:38:23,060
 o zaštiti tog života,

1032
00:38:23,460 --> 00:38:24,280
 i tvoja pozicija,

1033
00:38:24,280 --> 00:38:25,580
 da, koliko sam razumila,

1034
00:38:25,580 --> 00:38:27,080
 nisi za zakonsku zaštitu.

1035
00:38:27,080 --> 00:38:30,700
 I sad, kako sad ti to pomiruješ?

1036
00:38:30,700 --> 00:38:33,400
 Evo, kako to dvoje...

1037
00:38:33,400 --> 00:38:34,780
 Dakle, to je doista možda

1038
00:38:34,780 --> 00:38:35,660
 i najteže pitanje

1039
00:38:35,660 --> 00:38:36,220
 i evo tu,

1040
00:38:36,220 --> 00:38:38,800
 tu, evo,

1041
00:38:38,800 --> 00:38:40,420
 zašto ne mogu reći

1042
00:38:40,420 --> 00:38:42,280
 da sam desno ili ljevo.

1043
00:38:42,280 --> 00:38:45,500
 A puno sam o tome razmišljala

1044
00:38:45,500 --> 00:38:46,300
 i to je, recimo,

1045
00:38:46,300 --> 00:38:46,880
 jedna od stvari

1046
00:38:46,880 --> 00:38:47,880
 za koju sam smatrala

1047
00:38:47,880 --> 00:38:48,820
 da je potpuno promašeno

1048
00:38:48,820 --> 00:38:49,580
 o njoj govoriti

1049
00:38:49,580 --> 00:38:52,180
 za vrijeme predizborne kampanje,

1050
00:38:52,600 --> 00:38:54,420
 zato što se najosjetljivije

1051
00:38:54,420 --> 00:38:55,480
 i najvažnije pitanje,

1052
00:38:55,480 --> 00:38:57,560
 a to je zaštita života,

1053
00:38:57,560 --> 00:38:58,680
 banaliziralo

1054
00:38:58,680 --> 00:38:59,880
 i svelo na skupljanje

1055
00:38:59,880 --> 00:39:00,780
 političkih bodova.

1056
00:39:00,780 --> 00:39:02,320
 Sad, ja sam daleko od sveca

1057
00:39:02,320 --> 00:39:02,800
 i od nekoga

1058
00:39:02,800 --> 00:39:03,940
 ko isto u političkoj areni

1059
00:39:03,940 --> 00:39:05,180
 ne skuplja bodove,

1060
00:39:05,180 --> 00:39:07,680
 ali ipak mislim da neke teme

1061
00:39:07,680 --> 00:39:08,980
 trebaju zadržati dostojanstvo.

1062
00:39:08,980 --> 00:39:11,260
 Sad, kada govorimo

1063
00:39:11,260 --> 00:39:12,200
 o temi pobačaja,

1064
00:39:12,200 --> 00:39:13,600
 ne postoji ništa

1065
00:39:13,600 --> 00:39:14,620
 što je važnije od života

1066
00:39:14,620 --> 00:39:15,860
 i ne postoji ništa

1067
00:39:15,860 --> 00:39:17,780
 što je važnije štititi.

1068
00:39:17,780 --> 00:39:19,560
 I dakle, tu je

1069
00:39:19,560 --> 00:39:20,680
 na razini

1070
00:39:20,680 --> 00:39:22,420
 same abstrakcije

1071
00:39:22,420 --> 00:39:23,480
 i logike

1072
00:39:23,480 --> 00:39:24,600
 jedino

1073
00:39:24,600 --> 00:39:25,620
 ispravno rješenje

1074
00:39:25,620 --> 00:39:27,680
 potpuna i zakonska zaštita života.

1075
00:39:27,680 --> 00:39:29,320
 Međutim,

1076
00:39:29,320 --> 00:39:31,560
 kao netko tko

1077
00:39:31,560 --> 00:39:33,440
 živi u stvarnom svijetu

1078
00:39:33,440 --> 00:39:36,280
 i svjestanje kako taj svijet funkcionira,

1079
00:39:38,280 --> 00:39:40,040
 pola stoljeća

1080
00:39:40,040 --> 00:39:41,420
 ljudi su odgajani

1081
00:39:41,420 --> 00:39:44,640
 kao da je pobačaj nešto

1082
00:39:44,640 --> 00:39:46,340
 uobičajeno,

1083
00:39:46,340 --> 00:39:49,040
 svakome dostupno

1084
00:39:49,040 --> 00:39:50,740
 i nešto što se općenito

1085
00:39:50,740 --> 00:39:52,300
 učestalo događa.

1086
00:39:52,300 --> 00:39:54,120
 I u krajnjoj liniji

1087
00:39:54,120 --> 00:39:55,440
 kontracepcijsko sredstvo.

1088
00:39:55,440 --> 00:39:59,480
 I iz te pozicije

1089
00:39:59,480 --> 00:40:01,120
 doći i reći,

1090
00:40:01,120 --> 00:40:02,040
 prerezati,

1091
00:40:02,040 --> 00:40:04,100
 ja ne mislim da bi

1092
00:40:04,100 --> 00:40:05,480
 prvo da se može,

1093
00:40:05,480 --> 00:40:06,940
 a drugo da će imati

1094
00:40:06,940 --> 00:40:07,980
 pozitivne učinke.

1095
00:40:09,140 --> 00:40:09,680
 Što se tiče,

1096
00:40:09,680 --> 00:40:11,260
 ja inače općenito nisam sklona

1097
00:40:11,260 --> 00:40:15,460
 tome da drugima kažem

1098
00:40:15,460 --> 00:40:16,660
 što oni moraju učiniti.

1099
00:40:16,660 --> 00:40:19,400
 Ja samo mogu dati sve argumente

1100
00:40:19,400 --> 00:40:21,180
 zašto mislim da je nešto dobro

1101
00:40:21,180 --> 00:40:22,680
 i nešto loše.

1102
00:40:22,680 --> 00:40:24,640
 A odluka, konačna odluka

1103
00:40:24,640 --> 00:40:26,240
 će biti na tim ljudima,

1104
00:40:26,240 --> 00:40:28,720
 pogotovo u tako osjetljivim stvarima.

1105
00:40:28,720 --> 00:40:31,480
 I zaštita života je nešto

1106
00:40:31,480 --> 00:40:32,760
 što ja vjerujem da će

1107
00:40:32,760 --> 00:40:34,320
 evolutivnom svijesti

1108
00:40:34,320 --> 00:40:35,980
 na kraju prevladati.

1109
00:40:35,980 --> 00:40:37,660
 Jer mi smo danas u nekim

1110
00:40:37,660 --> 00:40:39,180
 paradoksalnim situacijama

1111
00:40:39,180 --> 00:40:40,820
 da smatramo da treba

1112
00:40:40,820 --> 00:40:42,820
 svaki životinski život štititi,

1113
00:40:42,820 --> 00:40:45,280
 a isto dobno ne želimo,

1114
00:40:45,280 --> 00:40:47,160
 premda nam je znanost odavno rekla

1115
00:40:47,160 --> 00:40:49,480
 kako rano počinje život

1116
00:40:49,480 --> 00:40:50,720
 i kako se brzo razvija,

1117
00:40:50,720 --> 00:40:52,940
 ne želimo štititi taj život od začeća.

1118
00:40:52,940 --> 00:40:54,520
 I mi ćemo doći do toga

1119
00:40:54,520 --> 00:40:56,260
 da se uskladimo s time.

1120
00:40:56,260 --> 00:40:57,080
 U krajnjoj liniji

1121
00:40:57,080 --> 00:40:58,820
 i kontracepcija je toliko razvijena

1122
00:40:58,820 --> 00:41:00,420
 da vi ne morate uopće doći

1123
00:41:00,420 --> 00:41:02,280
 u situaciju pobačaja.

1124
00:41:02,700 --> 00:41:04,460
 Samo još nismo na tom stupnju svijesti.

1125
00:41:05,220 --> 00:41:06,920
 A da bi došli do njega

1126
00:41:06,920 --> 00:41:08,260
 i da bi se

1127
00:41:08,260 --> 00:41:10,040
 islomili ti otpori,

1128
00:41:10,040 --> 00:41:12,600
 trebamo se otvoriti jedni prema drugima

1129
00:41:12,600 --> 00:41:15,600
 i nježno razgovarati.

1130
00:41:15,600 --> 00:41:17,220
 Ja doista mislim

1131
00:41:17,220 --> 00:41:18,380
 da kada se

1132
00:41:18,380 --> 00:41:21,240
 kada se ljudi otvori,

1133
00:41:21,240 --> 00:41:22,540
 kaže, ajmo, ozbiljno razgovarati,

1134
00:41:22,540 --> 00:41:24,620
 postoji samo jedan cilj u temi pobačaja.

1135
00:41:24,620 --> 00:41:26,100
 On je vrlo pragmatičan.

1136
00:41:26,620 --> 00:41:28,740
 A to je da pobačaj nestane,

1137
00:41:28,740 --> 00:41:30,740
 da ljudi ne čine pobačaj.

1138
00:41:30,740 --> 00:41:32,920
 Ili da je pobačaja što manje.

1139
00:41:32,920 --> 00:41:34,520
 To je ovaj drugi niži cilj.

1140
00:41:34,520 --> 00:41:36,180
 I onda je pitanje kako to ostvari.

1141
00:41:36,180 --> 00:41:38,640
 Ja mislim da se to može ostvariti

1142
00:41:38,640 --> 00:41:40,240
 i edukacijom i dialogom.

1143
00:41:40,240 --> 00:41:41,960
 I ako mi jedni u drugima

1144
00:41:41,960 --> 00:41:43,100
 prepoznamo ljude

1145
00:41:43,100 --> 00:41:44,320
 koji žele dobro,

1146
00:41:44,320 --> 00:41:45,980
 samo jedni govore iz pozicije

1147
00:41:45,980 --> 00:41:46,800
 zaštite žene,

1148
00:41:46,800 --> 00:41:49,440
 jer pobačaj je uopće bio dozvoljen,

1149
00:41:49,440 --> 00:41:50,900
 budimo realni.

1150
00:41:51,240 --> 00:41:52,920
 Zato što žena povijesno gledano

1151
00:41:52,920 --> 00:41:55,060
 nije imala mogućnost

1152
00:41:55,060 --> 00:41:56,720
 odlučivati o svojoj spolnosti

1153
00:41:56,720 --> 00:41:57,760
 i o svome tijelu.

1154
00:41:57,760 --> 00:41:59,700
 On je prvo kao politička odluka

1155
00:41:59,700 --> 00:42:01,840
